{"tid":328343,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"［求助］想發動技能但驚隻貓有人養","createTime":"2017-07-19T13:34:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-27T11:13:01.000Z","uid":3180,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fa6b02c24321cb221c4bdc6fb1b4a6ada8b136b0","tid":328343,"uid":3180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T13:34:28.000Z","msg":"係屯門置樂街市近動物診所附近洗衫，見到有隻貓女係度hea&amp;玩垃圾，本身睇佢唔到但Feel到有野望住我，我望返落地下見到佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/19/212917_d026a66d35fb683695c8fe3fa8e1553d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F19%2F212917_d026a66d35fb683695c8fe3fa8e1553d.jpg&h=f8baaf0e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/19/212928_7a6cd5186bfc34f242cd512d2a2ae96a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F19%2F212928_7a6cd5186bfc34f242cd512d2a2ae96a.jpg&h=1d1c01ef&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/19/213001_24ed014cd932e6762864d8264ab24ee0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F19%2F213001_24ed014cd932e6762864d8264ab24ee0.jpg&h=0d331317&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我又望實佢<br />\n好似平時同自己啲貓溝通咁引佢過黎俾我摸<br />\n但未試過同街貓玩眼神溝通<br />\n神奇既事發生了<br />\n佢衝埋黎撞我隻腳&amp;手逼我摸佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲發姣咁喵喵叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係勁似我屋企個兩隻野<br />\n岩岩望左眼仲以為啲貓跟我出門口洗衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f4015a52792dc9e7a2eea6c4197b92d2df37fb3","tid":328343,"uid":116300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T13:35:27.000Z","msg":"help push"},{"pid":"c3d447871e32b1a2e8ead157b7f8af9cccf66136","tid":328343,"uid":3180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T13:35:59.000Z","msg":"想問下附近居民有無見開呢隻野<br />\n有人養開就唔打擾佢了<br />\n無人養無野食個啲我先再執佢返去養"},{"pid":"b509a8e3dc9d17c3a700141c4ad727cdde7c653f","tid":328343,"uid":3180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T13:40:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"40503ea6ced1bdd62c8c59124befd26af25b7778","tid":328343,"uid":1558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T13:42:00.000Z","msg":"呢隻好似好耐架喇喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好地地由佢啦"},{"pid":"a0a076e5b1ddf1ea2988ead2999f0e62653d16c9","tid":328343,"uid":90646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T13:42:00.000Z","msg":"貓貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29150ab0fc3bc1617ead1eeb3620f000baeecc9a","tid":328343,"uid":3180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T13:43:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢隻好似好耐架喇喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好地地由佢啦</blockquote><br />\n咁由佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係諗緊嗲到咁又唔make sense<br />\n但又無掛頸圈"},{"pid":"353da1a9eb5cba1230ee33a4dd95762ea1474c32","tid":328343,"uid":1558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T13:46:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢隻好似好耐架喇喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好地地由佢啦</blockquote><br />\n咁由佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係諗緊嗲到咁又唔make sense<br />\n但又無掛頸圈</blockquote><br />\n前置樂丁丁表示置樂啲鋪貓唔係隻隻都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主你朝早留意下玉林苑燒味檔同埋果幾檔生果蔬菜檔，如果唔係果幾間就有有機會無人養"},{"pid":"75788a95dc27df421671d3c35e8279878ed25e5b","tid":328343,"uid":3180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T13:51:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢隻好似好耐架喇喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好地地由佢啦</blockquote><br />\n咁由佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係諗緊嗲到咁又唔make sense<br />\n但又無掛頸圈</blockquote><br />\n前置樂丁丁表示置樂啲鋪貓唔係隻隻都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主你朝早留意下玉林苑燒味檔同埋果幾檔生果蔬菜檔，如果唔係果幾間就有有機會無人養</blockquote><br />\n我好少去呢頭所以唔熟<br />\n最多一星期一次洗衫<br />\n黎親都收晒檔<br />\n係見過有黃貓係洗衣店露天泊車場摟人摸佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23735cef1765261a91b763c1f35dc9bcbee34032","tid":328343,"uid":45526,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T14:36:46.000Z","msg":"街貓好多時深夜會有餵貓姨姨餵<br />\n有心想養就夜晚搵下有無啲人餵貓問下<br />\n餵左咁耐忽然少左隻真係會好擔心"},{"pid":"3c0afb2a0299a3313215758645c1298d322a8c9c","tid":328343,"uid":45399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T03:47:25.000Z","msg":"我成日去睇佢地，夜晚先出黎，有個街市既婆婆睇住佢地，佢地有人餵食架"},{"pid":"53723a5535ca28e4dc25b3892431f2e2dcccdba3","tid":328343,"uid":96108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T08:17:35.000Z","msg":"佢哋喺度好多年啦，唔好搞佢哋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07efafd018a4f5348c14dba1b6ea9943f6d7eeb1","tid":328343,"uid":73730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T01:23:23.000Z","msg":"發動神通感應下佢本來係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ec8df16f1affdcf629b592f5e1264eedaec3b34","tid":328343,"uid":41784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T03:30:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/23/113015_5c60ae08dd23e0596880d6ae69c4ceca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F23%2F113015_5c60ae08dd23e0596880d6ae69c4ceca.jpg&h=b05d8111&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咪貨車後面啲鋪見到，如果係就唔好搞佢"},{"pid":"785f0f54dd3b9aa27eaed9821d2f372d224c1bb2","tid":328343,"uid":12449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T03:45:59.000Z","msg":"屌你 人地係條街好食好住 得閒又可以入鋪玩下 嘆下冷氣<br />\n冇啦啦捉人走 你話貓BB就要啫"},{"pid":"7b3256dc13f1e2592f3390560cda813ac734875d","tid":328343,"uid":45399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T11:13:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/27/191131_676599703662d4762e1bf39619169b30.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F27%2F191131_676599703662d4762e1bf39619169b30.jpg&h=edd71846&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/27/191132_5363511c544d90cee627544b8cc745b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F27%2F191132_5363511c544d90cee627544b8cc745b5.jpg&h=7fc3aa04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢好乖，街市係佢屋企，唔好攪佢地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}